<p>Eliminating Yosemite&#39;s Incrementing computer names, the real skinny on Yosemite and third-party SSDs, which codecs to use for creating your own streamable movies, advice on clean-installing and much, much more keep your geeks busy throughout this week&#39;s Mac Geek Gab episode. Download, press play and enjoy!</p>
